data.description: This cozy 3-bed, 2-bath home in Flour Bluff ISD offers comfortable living. A warm living space and modern kitchen greet you as you enter. The primary bedroom is spacious and features a luxurious bath with a stand-up shower and jet tub. The addition of solar panels and a backup battery provides eco-friendly and reliable power. The backyard is perfect for gardening and unwinding. Conveniently located near the Corpus Christi Naval Base, Laguna Madre, and North Padre Island.
